st no support :(   2/10Overall: 8/10I just can say if you love old games and like the way who JRPG's work this game is for you!If you want to have an running game with patches, multiplayer and 3D graphics go and play something else as this game wont make you have any fun!So far my review.Funfact: I bought this game 4 times on CD as i lost 1 and scratched 2 to death as i was much younger. But but now i got my last CD with the original how to printed on paper :)"
