76561198055693421,Recommended,253940,28109752,"Posted: 30 November, 2016",all,Dross,"Classic game by far.  However, it's somewhat of a pain to get the game to run correctly.  Install the game, manually install Directx and Quicktime from within the Septerra Core install folder, run and install the game as administrator, play the game with your onboard video adapter (right-click desktop and go to ATI/Nvidia control panel depending on what is installed) and select your Intel onboard graphics card to run the main Septerra Core .exe; newer cards will not play cinematics and will always cause seizure-inducing flashes on the screen during gameplay.  Thus, Intel HD Graphics x000 (2000, 3000, etc.) will run SC optimally.  Once the video issues are worked around, the game works awesome.  Happy oldschool Steampunk hunting!"
